Damage 12 - Delay 40<BR>
Weight: 9.9 - DEF, ERU, HEF, HUM, OGR, TRL<BR>
Classes: <a href="/shadow_knight/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">SHD</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/complete_healing.shtml?spellID=291">Complete Healing</a><BR>
Charges: 1<BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (Lore) <BR>
(STR +4) </font>
<BR>
Submitted By: Bugrup<BR>
<BR>
